# Kubernetes Pods

A Pod is the smallest deployable unit in Kubernetes.

A pod can contain one or more containers.

Containers inside a pod share

- network
- storage

Example Command

kubectl run nginx --image=nginx

Check pods

kubectl get pods

Describe pod

kubectl describe pod nginx
```

